{"tid":1544613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"召換 IT 巴絲幫手清算黑警","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:19:05.000Z","uid":36735,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab022cf8494ac64c41c4129736e50be7663c063a","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"各位大家好，係一個月前我開左個 post <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【我整合左個「清算黑警名單」】</span></span></strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372532/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372532/page/1</a>  <br />\n<br />\n用 Google PPT 列出黑警既罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，到而家已經有十多位巴絲加入，更有外國既巴打幫手做翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地每日馬不停蹄將黑警既罪行整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lErsYu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lErsYu&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=f761171b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lErsYu</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係黑警既行動力實在太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip; 我地面臨一個重大問題&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nPPT <span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">太多圖同埋 gif</span></span>，而家已經<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">超過 300 頁</span></span>&hellip; 就算 compress 左 d 圖都係 load 得好慢&hellip; 長遠好難再 share 比其他人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地懇求識寫網站、後台既巴絲幫手 develop 清算黑警既網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n知道其實有好多網站都有做黑警罪證既資料庫，但嘗試過聯絡無回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我地既手頭上既資料<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定係最多同更新密度最高</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地希望可以開發到個網站同埋 CMS，更容易將資料散播開去！<br />\n如果各位巴絲有興趣，請你 tg 聯絡我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"156b21c5d1f47c1e4ef8f0f02a70e26c36115214","tid":1544613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73a68c089845dfb452f8cae8c852ebfc55fc9c14","tid":1544613,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ebe3f76a7d7640d41a677325515bc5c64e1833","tid":1544613,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ab75eb5f0d5b5cd852d958f321632228b373f61","tid":1544613,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"推x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fcab19d210b855bd36f3a7903494f884dda1d0","tid":1544613,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"推x3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f75b56ebdfdb087d2ca7a3abc54284afe945273","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"73998e2148bc31aa29c4461f311d8309cda2de54","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"自推 1／10"},{"pid":"a3ac48a48b2cdce9856924776949aa398647eb28","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"自推 2／10"},{"pid":"5079cb8e710ec13202cb721c79e156603485fc69","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"自推 3／10"},{"pid":"40a4815f5c4066972fdc07a625e36689d1882cc7","tid":1544613,"uid":215340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8de2904b64b112149508f01b60a653c95fdecce7","tid":1544613,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"877641203a4e12345a919e01bfb4b08b62b649dd","tid":1544613,"uid":58987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://搵hkrev.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%90%B5hkrev.info&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c6152da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">搵hkrev.info</a>開個section"},{"pid":"bfa092340b0518d0d0665a80d07df3c74c4a7692","tid":1544613,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有fc既資料，有人證，有失蹤人口，有可疑既地方，大整合"},{"pid":"ecb9f52117ebc99d51523f82d28bbea60f25fd37","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877641203a4e12345a919e01bfb4b08b62b649dd","tid":1544613,"uid":58987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://搵hkrev.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%90%B5hkrev.info&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c6152da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">搵hkrev.info</a>開個section"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"有無佢地既 contact ？"},{"pid":"a6ea09d529fbcaf31e8b18095d8268cfcf0d7cd6","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"自推 4／10"},{"pid":"43532cc3ac551fd68572492af3ef5ff43e77181e","tid":1544613,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808577fe752b56d8467768d8be459102bfb9b396","tid":1544613,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"自推 5／10"},{"pid":"b111e5d4894d6ec4c80430cf7c156c3d9496dc5e","tid":1544613,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=